    public abstract class MessageHandler<TRequest extends com.google.protobuf.Message,TResponse extends com.google.protobuf.Message.Builder>
extends java.lang.Object
    Generic base class for all message handlers. It does the input marshaling, business logic as well as the output marshaling. Thread-Safety: Single thread.
